messages.message: Will try to do it in two separate tables! I’m also looking at long bank statement type documents, where tables break across several pages (i.e they are several different tables).  Conceptually there isn’t a difference between Table 1 on page 1 and Table 3 on page 3…is there a way to get them all?
i think that our table entity detection logic in AI Hub should be able to handle tables that span multiple pages - are you seeing that the table is extracted separately on each page?
